      "description": "Strength Saving Throw: DC [[lookup @save.dc.value activity=TQchFj2VXXJgU7Lq]], each [[lookup @target.affects.type activity=TQchFj2VXXJgU7Lq]] in the [[lookup @name lowercase]]{monster}'s space.\n\nFailure: [[/damage average activity=TQchFj2VXXJgU7Lq]] damage. If the target is a Large or smaller creature, it has the &amp;Reference[Grappled apply=false] condition (escape DC [[lookup @skills.ath.passive]]). Until the grapple ends, the target has the &amp;Reference[Restrained apply=false] condition, is &amp;Reference[suffocating]{suffocating} unless it can breathe water, and takes [[/damage average activity=khxVwH3AB0sx1qRG]] damage at the start of each of the [[lookup @name lowercase]]{monster}'s turns. The [[lookup @name lowercase]]{monster} can grapple one Large creature or up to two Medium or smaller creatures at a time with Whelm.\n\nAs an action, a creature within 5 feet of the [[lookup @name lowercase]]{monster} can pull a creature out of it by succeeding on a [[/check ath dc=@skills.ath.passive format=long]].\n\nSuccess: Half damage only.",
      "kind": "action",
      "legendary_cost": null,
      "name": "Whelm",
      "recharge": "4-6",
      "slug": "whelm",
      "uses_per_day": null
